I am interested in making an http call for storing the contact list.
And getting the list of the common people.

I will be needing an httpClient to make the call.

Now there can be two ways to make the call
1) Creating a thread in the main activity and making a call through it.
2) Having a dedicated service that will run in the background to retrieve the result.


MainActivity will start the HttpClientService once the button is clicked
and the service will start executing the client code to make an http call
and will return the result to the main activity
which will show the loader while the result is loading.
and once the results are load completely the service will be down and it will close.

